<Paragraph  FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">
    The following samples are available for this cateogry. 
</Paragraph> 
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Appearance</Bold> - Demonstrates the various properties available for customizing the appearance of an OlapChart</Paragraph>
