<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Series Customization</Bold> - Demonstrates customization of a chart series using series template binding.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Visual Styles</Bold> - Demonstrates customization of a chart skins using skin picker available in sample.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Watermark</Bold> - Illustrates how a text or image watermark can be added to a chart's background.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Chart Animations</Bold> - Illustrates different type of animations in OlapChart control for different series types.</Paragraph>
